    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1130741761">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1130741761" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1130741761" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1130741761">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1094172/">snooze</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-01-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">尽管十分细碎，但跟着年轻的托克维尔漫游美国，还是惊讶于他惊人的洞察力与明智的判断力。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

